column5: We are looking for a private owner cottage to rent on LOTW in the Kenora area next summer. Would any of you know of someone that has one? Thanks, Fred
This is in a very nice location near Andrews Bay and French Narrows. http://eagleislandfishing.com/
Here is a kenora real estate company that has rentals http://www.cabincountry.com/rentals.php

http://lowdpoa.com/ This association publishes a magazine about the LOTW area with a classified ad section. There always are ads for rentals. I don't think the magazine is online but I bet you could email them and see what is currently advertised. The Kenora Daily Miner newspaper and its sister publication The Lake of the Woods Enterprise are online and have ads from time to time for rentals. Enjoy your trip.
http://www.vrbo.com/vacation-rentals...e-of-the-woods I've had good luck with VRBO in other locales.
